Fast and Furious

   RÃ©sultat de recherche d'images pour "coccinelle"


   Fast and Furious



   Please

   Let us be slow and curious instead


   The world is running crazy

   Rushing till it crashes into a wall of pain

   I walk like a ladybug and breathe out

   I stop and face the sun

   Lie down, open my mind, palms to the sky


   Please

   Let us be nice and soft


   Welcoming the chirping of sparrows

   Paying attention to the caress of a spring breeze on my cheeks

   Spread the kind words and thank each day

   Lucky enough to live here in peace

   Eating peaches and kissing my babies


   Fast and Furious is no good to me

   Come and enjoy the shooting stars with me.


   CF

   (Inédit)

